[SHORT DESC]
Lowers foe's accuracy 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Lowers the target's accuracy one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Sand-attack has little to no competitive use. Using moves that affect accuracy is an ineffective strategy since many players switch their Pokemon out often, resetting the accuracy boosts. Its main use is to annoy new players in-game fighting puny Pidgey.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/flash">Flash</a> is a Normal-type equivalent.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/kinesis">Kinesis</a> is a Psychic-type equivalent.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/smokescreen">SmokeScreen</a> is a Normal-type equivalent.</p>